    Location retrieved from Facebook. This class is used to map venue, namedfacebooktype and other zillion different kinds of facebook locations to a single object.

    Conditional Elements

    • city
    • country
    • name
    • state
    Any of the conditional fields can be omitted, but at least one of the fields must be present.
